### Type class ordering information ###

order Data.IntSet.Internal.Eq___IntSet       Data.IntSet.Internal.Ord__IntSet
order Data.IntSet.Internal.Semigroup__IntSet Data.IntSet.Internal.Monoid__IntSet_mappend
